name: "Friday" movie sound-bites (interactive keyboard)
description:
This is an interactive NFT. Click on the Deebo image to start. Then you can click on any of the digital keys to play a sound-bite from the movie. There is also a backing music track that you can play too. And I also digitally painted the image of Craig and Smokey. 
The UI/UX was made with HTML, CSS, and Javascript. And I spent several hours collecting sound-bites and turning them into audio samples that I then assigned to keys on my MIDI keyboard. The backing music track is also original.

If the keys aren't working, try refreshing the page.
Have fun and enjoy!
www.theguidingrock.com
